    "title": "Mid-Level Frontend Developer at Sonata Software",
    "description": "Sonata Software, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Frontend Developer for our Gwalior operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sonata Software:\nSonata Software is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Troubleshoot, debug, and resolve software defects and performance issues\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Docker\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in TensorFlow\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Gwalior, Madhya Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sonata Software!",
